{"tid":1554574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請大家如果冇膽打狗，就唔好屌狗屌得咁撚興奮","createTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T05:20:49.000Z","uid":17812,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4b76f0c784ea90b4f71355ddbdd00a6016be2e","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"我見到嘅係<br />\n大家一見到狗就喪屌<br />\n（我明大家都好撚嬲，我都係）<br />\n<br />\n有時得幾隻狗，但有gear 有棍，大家以為安全喪屌<br />\n但當狗反cup 大家，個個就雞飛狗走<br />\n反而害咗啲想保護大家嘅手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該大家睇情況嚟屌呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhwXbKr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhwXbKr.jpg&h=4e451c60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"461a71a8e108d9e46cb80d575b6a56bb042325b4","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3860e100a1a71fddf38f877a472d3ddd2d18bd2f","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dda445ee097bf7ab2ce823f94d451204e1405d","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69b6245364af52b776100928750e5e112c8c2df","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdbf8ce6d86a981640871c12b7612bbe46d2911","tid":1554574,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/